Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂缚柩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来对付他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 请你做我的后援
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…砂…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.97,0:02:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来对付他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请当心点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人的攻击武器是骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像刚才那样射出自己的骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者从身体里抽出骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能自由地操纵骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂瀑我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如其名 你能操纵砂子是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最强对决 我爱罗对君麻吕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操纵砂子形成无懈可击的防御
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙不是近战的类型啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 要接近他很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十指穿弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方的动作干脆利落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是位很强的体术高手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻防一体 砂子攻守兼备吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 能控制的砂子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕只有葫芦里装的那些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂瀑我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可笑的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了砂子 你什么都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪你会背着这么重的砂子到处走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是最好的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂时雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平淡无奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有砂子 我什么都能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可笑的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从泥土里制造砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说只是雕虫小技
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用自己的砂子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把土里的岩石和矿物碾成砂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把自己的砂子混进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就有新的砂子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂瀑我爱罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是名不虚传啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂瀑送葬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一看到那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会想起那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和那家伙有着同样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想确认自己的生存价值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那种眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.85,0:06:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不讨厌黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗是养育我的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.45,0:08:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做错了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有神的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又把我困在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君麻吕 现在要用上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我们辉夜一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.25,0:09:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是现在的我唯一能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.72,0:10:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强大的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我没有立刻\N在皮层下用骨头制造出一层膜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顷刻间就会被你压成粉末
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨头 那家伙还真是个怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是副棘手的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太小看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不会再被砂子给困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流砂瀑流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这砂子的规模已经无法让人逃避或抵御了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个地貌完全改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂瀑大葬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我上次交手时相比更强了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 下一次我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个难缠的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就表示我还有活下去的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始要向雾隐发动夜袭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个事件发生后我们困扰了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今正是我们展示恐怖威力的绝好时机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那些家伙知道我们辉夜一族的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么 君麻吕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着想那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把出现在你面前的\N雾隐村的家伙杀光就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要按你的本能去行动就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾隐村的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.90,0:13:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么 再不斩先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间呆站着了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有着和我相同的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我没遇到再不斩先生之前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够性急的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是这个村子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目标就在旁边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 请过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能以战斗来维持自己的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一群蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会以杀戮为乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种单纯的东西已经跟不上时代了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把有组织的集团当作对手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算动手 也只是急着送死的蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活着的就剩这些了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来被包围了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防御比想像中的牢固
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 多杀一个是一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少让我开心一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何要战斗 自己又是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一无所知 只是一味地战斗下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要用到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为需要 这就是我行动的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 不战斗就活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也明白了这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一族中只有我幸存了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变得孤单一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤零零的 一味漫无目地徘徊着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.10,0:17:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的…花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会开在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.60,0:17:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连你也无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开在这里 不可能被人发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去没什么意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活下去也许就会找到有意思的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你找到了那朵花一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像我找到了你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然当时大蛇丸大人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但人是为了某种目的才降生于这个世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必定有着什么重要的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:19:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是守护大蛇丸大人以及他的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:20.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我回来 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 黑乎乎的 什么也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼神比我更炯炯有神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助现在身处黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁…宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里停止不前的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定追不上佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 你说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是停下来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧
